WEBVTT

00:03:28.667 --> 00:03:31.922
So of course, all his sensible
victims surrendered on sight.

00:03:32.646 --> 00:03:33.976
Put like that,

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:38.675
it's easy to see why Edward Teach
and his fellow pirates

00:03:38.699 --> 00:03:43.174
could be seen as pioneers
of modern communications design,

00:03:43.198 --> 00:03:45.122
and why their deadly symbol --

00:03:45.146 --> 00:03:46.208
(Laughter)

00:03:46.232 --> 00:03:47.383
there's more --

00:03:47.407 --> 00:03:50.392
why their deadly symbol
of the skull and crossbones

00:03:50.416 --> 00:03:52.706
was a precursor of today's logos,

00:03:52.730 --> 00:03:56.077
rather like the big red letters
standing behind me,

00:03:56.101 --> 00:03:58.280
but of course with a different message.

00:03:58.304 --> 00:03:59.308
(Laughter)

00:03:59.332 --> 00:04:02.342
Yet design was also used to nobler ends